                        <li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180115/022284.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/209/242/2259/146953394.jpg" alt="中华道学百问丨葛洪对医学的贡献主要表现在哪些方面？"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/daoxueyuan2015/daojiaochagnshi2015/list2015114153906.htm">道教常识</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180115/022284.htm">中华道学百问丨葛洪对医学的贡献主要表现在</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">葛洪，字稚川，东晋著名道士。著述颇丰，涵盖宗教、哲学、教育u、医学、炼丹等多个方面。他的医学成就和炼丹经验，对我国乃至世界的化学、冶炼、医药、科技等影响</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">李信军</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%81%93%E5%AD%A6" title="道学">道学</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E9%81%93%E5%AD%A6%E7%99%BE%E9%97%AE" title="中华道学百问">中华道学百问</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E8%91%9B%E6%B4%AA" title="葛洪">葛洪</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6%E8%B4%A1%E7%8C%AE" title="医学贡献">医学贡献</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<!--[if !IE]>|xGv00|7a2183cb5c299c90d185b09ceec7e37b<![endif]-->
                        <li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180604/027551.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/21/14/2279/148195566.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之错开天门道徒懒"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180604/027551.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之错开天门道</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明祖师有一位弟子名为冯阳贵，入道很早，人又勤奋好学，因此既留先天慧根，也有后天智性。于是，刘一明就助他开了天门，未曾想，开天门以后，道徒却预见未来，</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<!--[if !IE]>|xGv00|f224332de9ca8b1236b2291562ba8116<![endif]-->
                        <li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180206/014034.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/30/3/2263/147152370.jpg" alt="《驻云飞》（三十）丨丹道修真总结：作此一歌劝知音，直言无隐莫生怨"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/dandaoyangsheng2015/dandao2015/list2015114161401.htm">丹道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180206/014034.htm">《驻云飞》（三十）丨丹道修真总结：作此一</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">炼金丹者“法”的正确和“财”的有无，是判断丹法正歧的唯一标准。前面借助解读二十四首《驻云飞》的内容，就是希望通过悟元子宗师的权威影响力，去告诫道教修行者</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">袭明居士</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%81%93%E5%AD%A6" title="道学">道学</a></li>
