<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/030177.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/101/180/2277/148107926.jpg" alt="善道教化，为民所归：早期道教所致力的理想图景是什么？"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/daoxueyuan2015/daoxuelilun2015/list2015114154728.htm">道学理论</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/030177.htm">善道教化，为民所归：早期道教所致力的理想</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">学界一般认为东汉末年是道教组织的草创时期，而此时的天师道和太平道当为早期道教的代表。早期道教积极参与社会政治，以善道教化天下，倡导民众忏悔、治者仁心，在</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">清虚道人</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%A4%A9%E5%B8%88%E9%81%93" title="天师道">天师道</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E9%81%93" title="太平道">太平道</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E7%BB%8F" title="太平经">太平经</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%A4%BE%E4%BC%9A%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3" title="社会理想">社会理想</a></li>
