</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/026152.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/88/172/2277/148105873.png" alt="苦魂滞魄  乘光解脱：话说幽烛破暗的道教灯仪（下）"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/daoxueyuan2015/daoxuelilun2015/list2015114154728.htm">道学理论</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/026152.htm">苦魂滞魄  乘光解脱：话说幽烛破暗的道教</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">道教灯仪多种多样。本文具体介绍了分灯科仪、、破诸大地狱灯仪、血湖地狱灯仪等形式。可以说，透过密布在九幽地狱的重重阴霾，人们去能从种种灯仪中看到道教济世度</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">李远国 李黎鹤</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%81%AF%E4%BB%AA" title="灯仪">灯仪</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%8B" title="法事">法事</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%B3%95%E5%99%A8" title="法器">法器</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%AA" title="科仪">科仪</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/022870.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/196/168/2277/148104961.png" alt="苦魂滞魄  乘光解脱：话说幽烛破暗的道教灯仪（上）"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/daoxueyuan2015/daoxuelilun2015/list2015114154728.htm">道学理论</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/022870.htm">苦魂滞魄  乘光解脱：话说幽烛破暗的道教</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">灯是道教法事中频繁使用的法器。秦汉时代就有火祭的记载，灯也逐渐出现于皇家。而到了两晋南北朝时，灯进入平民的生活，而陆修静等高道也逐步发展出了灯仪。此外，</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">李远国 李黎鹤</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%81%AF%E4%BB%AA" title="灯仪">灯仪</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%8B" title="法事">法事</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%AA" title="科仪">科仪</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%B3%95%E5%99%A8" title="法器">法器</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180524/029516.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/58/131/2277/148095388.jpg" alt="从道家文献窥探原始记事与文字起源"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/daoxueyuan2015/daojiaochagnshi2015/list2015114153906.htm">道教常识</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180524/029516.htm">从道家文献窥探原始记事与文字起源</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">文字的起源问题一直扑朔迷离，学界尚未给出明确的定论。不过，可以通过对道家典籍进行分析，从侧面了解先民们的记事方式。本文则具体介绍了“八卦说”、“结绳说”</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">牧之</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%85%AB%E5%8D%A6" title="八卦">八卦</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%BB%93%E7%BB%B3" title="结绳">结绳</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97" title="文字">文字</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%81%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE" title="道家文献">道家文献</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
