                    <!-- 仙真高隐 -->
                    <ul>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180531/034959.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/234/150/2278/148165434.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之古稀将军引入道"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180531/034959.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之古稀将军引</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">宁夏将军兼甘肃提督苏宁阿素来仰慕周易文化。他曾于兴隆山听刘一明讲道，如痴如醉，遂请入家中细谈。由于刘一明看破他身患疾病，苏宁阿视刘一明若神人，奉其为师。</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180531/032337.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/83/147/2278/148164518.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之千里摄物救人命"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180531/032337.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之千里摄物救</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明不仅医术高明而且道法高深。一次，一女子突发急症，继续熊胆，而为了拿到熊胆，刘一明以千里摄物之术从秦州取来熊胆，救人一命。这既说明了刘一明医者仁心，</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180531/031805.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/134/146/2278/148164314.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之泉水山茶疗眼疾"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180531/031805.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之泉水山茶疗</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明医道高深，美名远扬。固原县县令曾借庙会的机会来寻觅祖师为妻子寻方，治疗眼疾。刘一明只是问了近况便推测出病情，随后以山泉水、山梅茶为药，借熏蒸、口服</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180530/031314.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/166/101/2278/148152871.jpg" alt="许逊高徒，滕王尊师：净明高道万振天师"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180530/031314.htm">许逊高徒，滕王尊师：净明高道万振天师</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">万振，又名万仞，为唐朝江西一带的知名高道，后被净明道尊奉。相传，他师从高道胡洞真，又有许逊传法的传说，因而道术十分高超。后来他往来于国家上层，曾做滕王之</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">万法勇</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E4%B8%87%E6%8C%AF" title="万振">万振</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%A4%A9%E5%B8%88" title="天师">天师</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%87%80%E6%98%8E%E9%81%93" title="净明道">净明道</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180529/009763.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/220/29/2278/148134565.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之一套功法医全村"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180529/009763.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之一套功法医</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明祖师常活动于兰州阿干镇和苑川河一带，并于此处行医治病。苑川河下游金家崖村的人们因饮食习惯多有胃病，而刘一明祖师了解以后，就传授了一套功法，让他们练</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180528/031157.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/185/10/2278/148129685.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之隔山发功疗疾病"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180528/031157.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之隔山发功疗</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">贡马井有一位名为东生的小伙子因勤劳能干娶回了地主家的女儿十月。一家人其乐融融却突遭横祸，十月长出了乳腺瘤。无奈下，东生求医于祖师，而祖师隔山发功，治好了</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
<ul class="second">
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180528/030591.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/70/9/2278/148129315.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之传功谢祥疗疾病"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180528/030591.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之传功谢祥疗</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">谢祥是刘一明的俗家密友，多次捐助银两以供刘一明修观置田。谢祥体弱多病，多方诊治仍旧没有好转，后来求医于刘一明。刘一明传其性命之功，从而治好了多年疾病，因</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180528/029088.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/203/5/2278/148128428.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之白骡徒儿前世债"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180528/029088.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之白骡徒儿前</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明祖师有一徒弟，名为陆旋。他聪明伶俐，做事认真，可惜却骄傲自大，走上了为恶之途。他死后化为白骡以赎债。刘一明祖师听闻此事，就亲去查看，帮徒弟还了债务</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180528/028012.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/5/3/2278/148127720.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之三遇纯阳吕洞宾"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180528/028012.htm">刘一明祖师传丨祖师传说至今传之三遇纯阳吕</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明祖师其实也是一个人，也有七情六欲。相传，他一生三次遇到吕洞宾点化自己，无奈“修道图虚荣”，一一错过。此后，刘一明祖师与世俗断绝往来，每日只参悟妙道</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/031520.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/12/183/2277/148108602.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨修造著述功圆满之辛劳一生终羽化"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/031520.htm">刘一明祖师传丨修造著述功圆满之辛劳一生终</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">直到羽化前两年，刘一明仍旧笔耕不辍，著书立说。清宣宗道光元年（1821年），八十八岁高龄的高道刘一明，自知不久将升登天阙，归于大道，于是召集弟子，加以训</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/028830.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/197/177/2277/148107257.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨修造著述功圆满之年已耄耋犹不歇"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/028830.htm">刘一明祖师传丨修造著述功圆满之年已耄耋犹</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">玉皇行宫建成，丛林制度设立，但是刘一明祖师还是没有停下脚步。嘉庆十八年，刘一明已过八旬，仍积极投身于当地的宫观修缮、修路造桥等工作。他一生参与修建、复兴</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">贾来生</span><ul class="clearfix"><li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%88%98%E4%B8%80%E6%98%8E%E7%A5%96%E5%B8%88%E4%BC%A0" title="刘一明祖师传">刘一明祖师传</a></li></ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/019188.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/242/161/2277/148103222.jpg" alt="刘一明祖师传丨修造著述功圆满之兴办丛林定戒律"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/xianzhengaoyin2015/gaodao2015/list201511416934.htm">高道</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/019188.htm">刘一明祖师传丨修造著述功圆满之兴办丛林定</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">刘一明一生高风亮节，三教圆融，有一代宗师之风，然而这并不能保证他的弟子们也能如此。为了让弟子们“人人循规蹈矩，登乎彼岸”，他兴建丛林制度并振兴戒律以规范</div>
