<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/minsudaoyi2015/wenyi2015/list2015114162324.htm">文艺</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180412/018572.htm">大梦谁先觉：《头号玩家》中的道家智慧</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">近日上映的《头号玩家》深受好评，而斯皮尔伯格在电影中的设定却蕴含着古老的道家智慧：“反者道之动”的辩证关系，“自然无为”的开放豁达，梦与醒之间的重复关系</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">牧之</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1" title="电影">电影</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E8%BE%A9%E8%AF%81" title="辩证">辩证</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%97%A0%E4%B8%BA" title="无为">无为</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%A2%A6" title="梦">梦</a></li>
</ul>
<a target="_blank" class="comments" href="/a/20180412/018572.htm">3</a>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180409/019734.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/157/105/2270/147633682.jpg" alt="道家者流，衣裳楚楚——浅析范仲淹《道服赞》"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/minsudaoyi2015/list20151116151630.htm">书画</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180409/019734.htm">道家者流，衣裳楚楚——浅析范仲淹《道服赞</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">近日，范仲淹《道服赞》书卷在北京故宫博物院展出。这卷书法作品展现出北宋时期文人们好穿道服的文雅风俗，也体现了范仲淹抚琴谈易，充满道家豁达之气的另一面。</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">止水</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%81%93%E6%9C%8D" title="道服">道服</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E8%8C%83%E4%BB%B2%E6%B7%B9" title="范仲淹">范仲淹</a></li>
</ul>
<a target="_blank" class="comments" href="/a/20180409/019734.htm">1</a>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
